articles.title: Watch: Ben Stokes finally ends epic Usman Khawaja resistance with cunning slower ball - Wisden
articles.description: Watch: In an inspired bowling change, Ben Stokes brought himself on and got Usman Khawaja to drag one back onto his stumps to end his long vigil at the crease in the second innings of the first Ashes Test at Edgbaston.
